<h1 class="entry-title page-title">Asymptomatic transmission of COVID-19 didn’t occur at all, study of 10 million finds</h1>
<hr class="single-header">
<div class="entry-excerpt">Only 300 asymptomatic cases in the study of nearly 10 million were discovered, and none of those tested positive for COVID-19.</div>
</header>

<br>
